Simona Paggi is an Italian film editor. She was nominated for the Academy Award for Film Editing for her work in the film Life Is Beautiful (1997). She won the David di Donatello for Best Editing for her work in The Stolen Children (1992) 
I read the paragraph on http://wikipedia.org
